===Etymology===
From {{bor|en|NL.|ephemerus}}, from {{der|en|grc|ἐφήμερος}}, the more common form of {{m|grc|ἐφημέριος||of, for, or during the day, living or lasting but for a day, short-lived, temporary}}, from {{m|grc|ἐπί||on}} + {{m|grc|ἡμέρα||day}}.

